Call Box exists to grow people. Our culture promotes a "work hard, play hard" mentality that offers growth opportunities for employees both inside and outside the office. We hire smart and ambitious doers and set them loose in an exciting and complex business environment where they will build, sell, and deploy Artificial Intelligence technology solutions. Our solutions attack one of the biggest business problems in existence today: the phone. 
As an Accounting Associate, you will assist in the monthly invoicing process, customer collections, payroll activities, accounts payable, HR functions, and other administrative duties. 
You will be a key member of a dynamic, small but growing team. 
